node.text:
When I got to Winnipeg at 18 years old, I didn't know what to expect. It became clear very quickly that this city loved hockey more than anything else. I couldn't have asked for a more loyal, dedicated and passionate fanbase. Thank you to all the Jets fans who took me in and made my family and I feel welcome. 

Thank you to the entire front office for drafting me in 2016 and giving me the opportunity to live my dream of being an NHL player.

To my coaches, trainers and the support staff, I appreciate everything you have done for me. Thank you for showing me how to be a professional and helping me succeed on and off the ice. 

To all my Jets teammates over the past five seasons, it was an honor to play with you.

Columbus- I'm ready to get to work and I'm very excited to be a part of this franchise. Blue Jackets fans, get ready. #CBJ

node.text:
CHARITY AUCTION TIME! INFORMATION IN ENGLISH BELOW.
Lauantaina tehdään taas hyvää! Hyväntekeväisyyshuutokaupassamme on huudettavana mm. mun viime kaudella käyttämät kustomoidut luistimet, joita ei muualta saa! Lisäksi huudettavana on mm. Auston Matthewsin maila nimmarilla, golfkierros mun ja Sami Välimäen kanssa, tennikset Sashan kanssa, Sashan nimmarilla varustettu maila, Miro Heiskasen autenttinen fanipaita nimmarilla ja kaiken kruunaa yhteiset jäät Sashan ja mun kaa enintään neljälle hengelle! Tarjouksia voi jättää myös etänä, tiedustelut ja yhteydenotot info@lainebarkovcharity.fi. Keräämme huutokaupan avulla varoja Laine & Barkov Charity Golfin hyväntekeväisyyspottiin, joka lahjoitetaan Tampereen Kehitysvammaisten Tuki ry:n toimintaan.
This Saturday we are hosting a charity golf event with my friend Aleksander Barkov. We will be auctioning my game worn customized skates from last season, Auston Matthews’ signed stick, Barkov’s signed stick, a signed authentic fan jersey from me, and some VIP experiences like golf and tennis with me or Barkov. If you want, you can bid remotely! Inquiries via email to info@lainebarkovcharity.fi. The proceeds of the auction will benefit The Tampere Association for Persons with Intellectual Disabilities.

#lainebarkovcharity #laine #barkov #nokiarivergolf #charityauction #gameworn
